    <!-- Taken from http://www.windriver.com/products/titanium-server/ -->
    <p>For installation and maintenance, HPE Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade consists of three logical
      or conceptual <i>regions</i>: Non-KVM, KVM, and baremetal.</p>
    <p>The Baremetal region leverages the OpenStack Ironic service, which aims to provision bare
      metal machines instead of virtual machines.</p>
    <p><b>Note:</b> These regions do not function as OpenStack regions. </p>
